@BitPaine @CanadianSatoshi @Strategy People ask why MSTR should have a premium.

Maintaining a USD reserve, and a number of highly liquid capital market tools (common stock, BTC holdings, preferreds, debt) and being willing to do counter-cyclical things with those tools, is the good-optics answer to that question.

